Package eu.profinit.manta.connector.powerdesigner.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CompositeModelObject<T extends SimpleModelObject>
    Composite object in a data model has metadata, can be mapped to composite objects and contains simple objects.
    DataModel
    A data model is a representation of the information consumed and produced by a system, which lets you analyze the data objects present in the system and the relationships between them.
    Entity<E extends Entity<E,S>,S extends SimpleModelObject>
    An entity represents an object about which you want to store information.
    Mappable
    Interface for getting information about mappings of an object.
    NamedObject
    Interesting properties of an object from PowerDesigner's data model.
    Schema<C extends CompositeModelObject<S>,S extends SimpleModelObject>
    Schema is a container for composite objects.
    SimpleModelObject
    Simple object is a set of metadata that can be mapped to another simple object.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Layer
    Possible levels of abstraction of data models and underlying objects.
